ygData.messageBody:
Well if you're having problems finding a group, I personally soloed in west
commmons near the east commons zone wall (the non desert side). I just
pulled yk's and giant spiders and darkweeds. These give good exp plus you
get some cash from selling fangs and silk/venom sacs :) Once you hit 14, its
a breeze. I made level 15 in 5 hours ;)
Allsar Olath`Vlos - Rathe
